yep your eyes are not deceiving you guys. next week we're celebrating two important national day, one is the International Labour Day (Hari Buruh Internasional) and National Education Day (Hari Pendidikan Nasional), respectively on 1st and 2nd of May 2025.

since I personally (you guys are welcome disagreeing with this ofc) believe these two topics are somewhat correlate and intersect each other, what do you guys reflect or what's on your mind coming onto these two national day?
